    "name": "Razorpay API Collection",
    "description": "A comprehensive Postman collection for Razorpay's payment gateway APIs, covering Payments, Orders, Customers, Invoices, Subscriptions, Payment Links, and RazorpayX Payouts. Uses https://api.razorpay.com/v1/ for most endpoints, with v2 for Route. Requires Basic Authentication with Base64-encoded API key (key_id:key_secret) from Razorpay Dashboard. Supports test mode for safe testing. All responses are JSON. Covers all major public APIs as of August 2025, based on official documentation and Razorpay Postman Public Workspace.",
